第三步：创建Deployment
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: yolo
spec:
  replicas: 2
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: yolo
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: yolo
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: yolo
        image: yolo:v1
部署：
kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml
第四步：创建Service
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: yolo-service
spec:
  selector:
    app: yolo
  ports:
  - port: 80
    targetPort: 8000
部署：
kubectl apply -f service.yaml
